hopobject.body: Could you please repeat that? animedonline.com.br This list of accomplishments has never been simply about getting the President a second term. This guy is going to leave a legacy, and it is starting to look like a really good one. I know some progressives consider him a "disappointment," but these are folks who are looking for that unicorn. They like to put pressure on Blue Dogs and in the process help the right wing Republicans win election after election.
